Netflix is a video streaming application that allows you access to the service's huge library of movies and TV shows. Netflix gets a Windows Modern UI application for Windows 8 with a beautiful interface.ou can pin the Netflix app on either side of the screen to continue watching video in a small screen while using another application. Alternatively, you can have Netflix as the main app and pin another app next to it to multitask with Netflix in a bigger window.
